 3. Add MySQl resources: resources/
  - Add application-mysal.properties 
  - add data.sql
  - add schema.sql
 
 4. How to check MySQL Database
  4.1 Go to Run menu --> Run Configuration  --> Change Arguement
      -> input "--spring.profiles.active=mysql" --> apply --> Run
  4.2 Open mysql command tools
   -> mysql -uroot -p
   -> Enter password:xxxx
   -> show databases;
   -> use cars;
   -> show tables;
   -> select * from car;